{
  "stem": "15694.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I had to sit the ledge of the-- the edge of the wagon with the bundle over the buffers, and my feet against them, holding my self and balancing the way I wouldn't want my children to imitate me.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And suddenly, one of the branches got loose and danced on the buffer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It-- each time the rails met, there's a little hum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now they're trying to do away with it in-- in-- and-- sort of in Germany, it was a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now they do it away with it as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You don't-- you don't-- it's quite smooth now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If you go certain stretches by rail, other stretches are still not-- you know, still under with those connecting rails.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyway, these hums cause the wood to jump.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it was dancing to the left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I thought it's going to fall and perhaps derail the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It started jumping again to the right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And a few times-- and each time I started sweating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, it if derails the train, will it kill us all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I managed at one stage when it was rather in-- in the middle to put my foot against it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But other pieces which I had loosened when I took away my foot managed to fall free, but harmlessly under the train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, this little episode will come later back into our mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And anyway, this-- of course-- wood for the winter, was never to be enjoyed by us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But who it would be enjoyed, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My father was working with me already in the ammunition camp of-- of Klaj.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And on the 24th there was a transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we were told not to come back home anymore at-- in evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We-- they prepared barracks for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
